  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Quality Assurance Assistant Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>This role supports compliance with regulations, promotes a culture of continuous improvement, and safeguards workplace safety and the environment within the business operations. Collaborate cross-functionally to drive continuous to quality, Halal, workplace safety and sustainability compliance. </strong></p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><p><u>Food Safety & Hygiene Management</u></p><ul><li>Maintain and monitor the Food Safety Management System (FSMS) in accordance with HACCP, ISO 22000 and other applicable international food safety standards required by business operations.</li><li>Conduct routine hygiene inspections (internal and external sites), internal audits and verification activities to ensure compliance with food safety, hygiene, sanitation and regulatory requirement. </li><li>Monitor and verify CCPs and OPRPs, temperature control, cleaning and sanitation programs, pest control, and waste management systems.</li><li>Assist in the investigation of food safety incidents, customer complaints, and non-conformities, including root cause analysis and implementation of corrective actions. </li><li>Develop and implement SOPs for food operations. </li><li>Conduct food safety, hygiene and SOP training for food handlers and operational staff to ensure compliance.</li><li>Support product quality assurance initiatives to ensure consistent quality and regulatory compliance.</li><li>Facilitate internal and external inspection / audits (certification bodies and regulatory agencies). </li></ul><p><u>Halal Assurance Management </u></p><ul><li>Ensure the compliance in Halal Certifications Conditions. </li><li>Act as Halal Assurance Officer and assist in overseeing Halal compliance in operations, documentation and audits. </li><li>Facilitate Halal audits and ensure corrective actions are implemented effectively. </li></ul><p><u>Work Safety and Environment Compliance</u></p><ul><li>Monitor and identify workplace hazards for improvement. </li><li>Support the implementation and continual improvement of sustainability initiatives, including waste reduction, resource efficiency, and environmentally responsible practices.</li><li>Perform any other duties and responsibilities as assigned by superior to support the achievement of the Company’s food safety, quality assurance, hygiene, work safety and sustainability objectives.</li></ul><p><strong>Whatsapp 91834574 for more information</strong></p>",
